{"tid":1674553,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"美國人權民主法案制裁名單 其實應該要有CCTVB","createTime":"2019-10-25T09:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T13:12:45.000Z","uid":293667,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bb09268448ee75779565ebef3a6767f3c3ea15eb","tid":1674553,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:26:34.000Z","msg":"某程度上成件事搞到咁 <br />\nCCTVB係有唔少責任 新聞幫哂政府 偏頗報導<br />\n某些報導係直頭唔講 好似警察控制哂咁<br />\n如果佢地一開始唔咁做 而係正氣d既話<br />\n播黑警d做事手法同中立d<br />\n應該會無咁多藍絲 同政府應該一早會跪低<br />\nCCTVB先係終極既亂港分子<br />\n所以話人權法點少得CCTVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff3185c34b11e121be99466d72fdd92e918194b7","tid":1674553,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:26:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9dc3c33f20750557bd796e0b9ce40e717bc81eb","tid":1674553,"uid":129134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:34:17.000Z","msg":"TVB袁志偉根正苗紅到連兩個仔英文名都係普通話拼音<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1667979\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1667979</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c82c404f712ab47ec84fdcd78d08a60040dcee15","tid":1674553,"uid":293667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:35:45.000Z","msg":"CCTVB嚴重侵犯第四權<br />\n做政府既走狗 無可能咁樣比佢冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8b196513317f306552e10d0f5acded02ed6851","tid":1674553,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T09:36:09.000Z","msg":"仆街cctvb <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61de5f50aec1e76717f562c9574ce8a8354be36e","tid":1674553,"